A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Local Government – Fees, Receipts, and Penalties for Plastic and Paper
3 Carryout Bags
4 FOR the purpose of requiring certain retailers that charge a fee for providing a plastic or
5 paper carryout bag to a customer under a local law to provide a receipt to a customer
6 that includes the fee amount charged and the number of bags issued to the customer;
7 and generally relating to local fees for plastic and paper carryout bags.
8 BY adding to
9 Article – Local Government
10 Section 1–1321
11 Annotated Code of Maryland
12 (2013 Volume and 2024 Supplement)
